ATC (Anatomical Therapeutic Chemical Classification)
----------------------------------------------------

ATC codes are maintained by the World Health Organization Collaborating
Centre for Drug Statistics Methodology (WHOCC). The ATC codes in this
repository are obtained via Wikidata (CC0) and are used solely as
identifiers for cross-referencing pharmacological substances.

